data.title: Recipes – Joy in the Meantime
data.text:
Creamy Mushroom and White Bean Stew

Crafted with love and the earthy goodness of mushrooms, tender baby potatoes, and creamy white beans, this stew is a testament to the power of simple ingredients coming together to create something truly magical. Infused with the aromatic delight of thyme and rosemary, each spoonful is a celebration of flavor and texture, promising to warm your heart and soul.

Valentine’s Day Popcorn Mix

Make this fun and festive Valentine’s Day Popcorn Mix for a sweet and salty treat perfect for parties, movie nights, and more!

Whole30 Pan Roasted Chicken Breast Recipe

This Pan Roasted Chicken Breast Recipe is the quickest, tastiest, and easiest chicken recipe you’ll ever make! Add it to your weekly meal prep for healthy salads, quesadillas, nachos, soups, and more!

Perfect Baked Chicken Meatballs (Whole30, Paleo, Keto)

These Perfect Whole30 Baked Chicken Meatballs are made with simple ingredients for a super versatile recipe perfect for game day appetizers, office lunches, and more!

Simple Fall Salad Recipe

This Simple Fall Salad is made in minutes with fresh, seasonal produce for a healthy Whole30 meal you’ll be excited to eat!

Paleo Butternut Squash Soup with Crispy Pork

Made with fresh produce and warm fall flavors, this Paleo Butternut Squash Soup recipe is topped with crispy pork for a tasty comfort food recipe perfect for weeknight dinners! Omit the pork for a vegetarian option.

Instant Pot Tangy Whole30 Chicken

This Insant Pot Tangy Whole30 Chicken is made with simple, low carb ingredients for a fast and easy recipe perfect for your weekly meal prep!

Whole30 Breakfast Sausage

These Whole30 Breakfast Sausages are the perfect high protein meal prep recipe for easy breakfasts or quick dinners that are kid-friendly and delicious!

Perfect Shrimp Burgers

Made with simple ingredients, these Perfect Shrimp Burgers are served with a homemade tartar sauce recipe for a low carb, Whole30 friendly meal perfect for every occasion. Make them ahead of time for easy meal prep or quick dinners!

Peach Caprese Salad

Made with fresh ingredients and ready in minutes, this Peach Caprese Salad is the easiest summer recipe everyone will love. Serve it as a healthy appetizer or light side dish to have all your guests raving!
